{"tid":522283,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明連登點解咁憎DC9","createTime":"2018-01-07T11:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T22:26:09.000Z","uid":73231,"like":38,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1bf7468ee784c8a4600d4085f46706478b3591","tid":522283,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"好日都唔返香港一次<br />\n<br />\n自己又唔識路 而香港的士算係平（一程兩個女仔分每人十幾廿蚊HKD，仲平過美國搭巴士）<br />\n又唔使拎住咁多嘢就每次返嚟都搭十次八次的士<br />\n以往對的士佬冇乜特別壞印象<br />\n<br />\n今日返嚟有一半的士cum旗但又會停低問小姐你去邊？<br />\n酒店bell desk 幫手截的士個的士佬離遠開窗大聲問係咪過海<br />\n之後左穿右插仲衰過加州啲司機<br />\n仲要開住跑馬大大聲<br />\n一到紅燈拎住成份報紙睇馬經<br />\n仲一邊用倒後鏡喪𥄫我哋條短裙<br />\n好明顯吓<br />\n<br />\n上次返嚟都唔係咁 的士做乜越來越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cc265b8d5ffd2c41b9db8da9f82acf850a5a39","tid":522283,"uid":143454,"like":0,"dislike":62,"score":-62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce6987b05f606f23d6598b3955f4547277b78149","tid":522283,"uid":73231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06cc265b8d5ffd2c41b9db8da9f82acf850a5a39","tid":522283,"uid":143454,"like":0,"dislike":62,"score":-62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:49:11.000Z","msg":"原來你條變態佬係揸的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371c4972704ccfe700ba97ccbbd726f1726d3ffc","tid":522283,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊DC系統"},{"pid":"314e653b0b319dedf6de5ee37dd8857cefea2f45","tid":522283,"uid":146917,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"男人老狗著短裙係人都望啦"},{"pid":"2563860f3f057fd374c3332370f5442ce8ae8f53","tid":522283,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"314e653b0b319dedf6de5ee37dd8857cefea2f45","tid":522283,"uid":146917,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:56:55.000Z","m